Cell["\<\
This lecture is supported by a hands-on tutorial 9 to construct a ML model to \
predict the Outcome of a treatment for depression. Prior to constructing the \
model, in this  tutorial we will also deal with data cleaning, \
pre-processing, exploration, statistical analysis, practicing the standard \
route to modelling.  \
\>", "Subsubitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778568373771381*^9, 3.778568459802706*^9}, {
