  3.9472339854549026`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7c45c476-91c0-455a-b890-\
0039ba823a91"],

Cell["\<\
This your opportunity to learn about Database Management Systems, SQL and \
Mongo.  \
\>", "Subsubitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778568373771381*^9, 3.778568459802706*^9}, {
