  3.977216182965797*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9c6b970b-f829-440a-a52f-\
5f4d85a52290"],

Cell["\<\
This course will provide you with a global view about what data science is, \
the tools and the analysis you need to do solve a data-based problem    \
\>", "Subsubitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778568373771381*^9, 3.778568459802706*^9}, {
