2b92175ad6b1"],

Cell["\<\
Essential and complementary references can be accessed in our Leganto Reading \
list, which can be accessed from our course Myaberdeen Webpage. \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808549465569303*^9, 3.808549486135639*^9}, {
  3.808550760462145*^9, 3.808550763306376*^9}, {3.811579042436811*^9, 
